181122102925-statue-of-liberty-crown.title: Taco Bell
181122102925-statue-of-liberty-crown.text: Two Taco bells in one day. This place Didn't have ready what I wanted so they cooked it fresh just like they should, Then I got all my condiments and needed napkins / silverware in the bag. I am impressed and Will be back
181122102925-statue-of-liberty-crown.author: Order

170321135754-airport-security-line.title: Mcdonald's
170321135754-airport-security-line.text: We started with scallion pancakes and dumplings. Both were fantastic. Both were extremely delicious with just the right amount of crunch. I loved my Singapore noodles - so flavorful and filled with veggies and a combination of meats. My son couldn't stop eating his beef brisket noodle soup - so much flavor thanks to the broth and fried garlic. My son enjoyed his Zheng Cafe Seattle style egg foo young over rice. And my hubby enjoyed his ribeye steak with black pepper sauce. We also enjoyed the complimentary dessert.
170321135754-airport-security-line.author: Order

181119170125-ploughgate-creamery-butter-.title: Shake Shack
181119170125-ploughgate-creamery-butter-.text: Very nice place to get authentic asian cuisine. All sorts of vegan options. The restaurant is vegetarian normally and has a full vegan menu with all the fixings. We started off with the fried spring rolls and they were very good. Main course we tried the pan fried noodles with tofu and my partner ordered the full house mix with all sorts of goodness.
181119170125-ploughgate-creamery-butter-.author: Order

181121164246-boeing-777-9x-assembly-1.title: Li'l Woody's
181121164246-boeing-777-9x-assembly-1.text: I just liked their dishes. I always get great customer service there. The place is well kept and the staff members are always nice. Would recommend to others.
181121164246-boeing-777-9x-assembly-1.author: Order

170301162422-leaning-tower.title: Subway
170301162422-leaning-tower.text: The food was delicious!I ordered a bowl of Dan dan noodles and some fried dumplings.Quite tasty .However,the food did not include some veggies which made it became unhealthy and the fried dumplings were a little bit oily.The space inside the restaurant was limited too.I mean...this restaurant's services can be improved for a little bit to become perfect.
170301162422-leaning-tower.author: Order

181118211616-banasthali-vidyapith-aviati.title: Dick's Drive-In
181118211616-banasthali-vidyapith-aviati.text: My favorite fast lunch, and shockingly authentic-ish Chinese food (sitting next to General's Chicken, but hey). I love the pork, the eggs, and the veggies. Happy hour $2 off per pound is one of the best deals in town. I love this place!
181118211616-banasthali-vidyapith-aviati.author: Order
